<span class="cushycms"><h1><br />
<br />
Welcome to the Loring, Port Loring and District (Argyle) Community Library</h1>

<p>We are located in the Argyle Public School. Our library is operated in partnership with the Near North District School Board and the Local Services Board.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;</p>
